Introduction

Athena Yang is a South Korean-Swedish singer and composer under ATTRAKT. She is best known as the main dancer, sub vocalist, visual and maknae of the girl group FIFTY FIFTY.

On August 11, 2024, Athena was the second member of FIFTY FIFTY to be revealed. She debuted on August 30, 2024, with the group's pre-release single "Starry Night".
